        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-679",
        "content": "Carrying the bag with its indisputable proof of some person's guilt, we made our way through the familiar corridor by the dressing rooms, out under the roof of the so-called large studio.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
